text: is a cape located in the Kii Peninsula in Shima, Mie in Japan. == The lighthouse == The lighthouse of Cape Daiō was built in 1927.. It was damaged by aerial bombardment during the Pacific War (1941-1945) and by the passage of Typhoon Vera in 1959. The limestone structure visible in 2015 is a renovated version of the original dating back to 1978. == References == Daio Category:Landforms of Mie Prefecture
